text: Thongloun Sisoulith , (; born 10 November 1946) is a Laotian politician. In 2021, he became the President of Laos. He was the Prime Minister of Laos from 2016 until 2021. ==Related pages== *General Secretary of the Lao People's Revolutionary Party ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Current national leaders Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Laos Category:Prime Ministers of Laos
